# Performance Horizon Public API

# Data Structures

## Address (object)
+ address1: Gardegasse 11 - 1st line of the address
+ address2: Top 7 (nullable) - 2nd line of the address
+ address3: New York (nullable) - 3rd line of the address
+ address4 (nullable) - 4th line of the address
+ country: JP - Country of the address
+ postcode: `A-101` - Postcode/Zipcode attached to the address

